00:01:47.010 --> 00:01:49.590
I was a foreign
correspondent in Rome.

00:01:49.590 --> 00:01:52.830
I covered the Vatican,
which I thought

00:01:52.830 --> 00:01:56.780
was the most secretive
bureaucracy on the planet.

00:01:56.780 --> 00:01:58.530
And then I realized
the Board of Education

00:01:58.530 --> 00:02:00.420
is even more
secretive and complex.

00:02:00.420 --> 00:02:03.900
So I thought if I had
trouble, other people

00:02:03.900 --> 00:02:06.060
might have trouble too.

00:02:06.060 --> 00:02:09.120
And I started writing
the books then.

00:02:09.120 --> 00:02:12.990
A couple years later, we set
