00:52:03.790 --> 00:52:08.242
and how effective they are for
native speakers of English?

00:52:08.242 --> 00:52:09.700
CLARA HEMPHILL:
Very good question,

00:52:09.700 --> 00:52:11.920
so in the index of
the book, you'll

00:52:11.920 --> 00:52:14.330
find dual-language programs.

00:52:14.330 --> 00:52:20.020
There's Chinese, Spanish,
