00:52:34.960 --> 00:52:38.320
speak the other language, and
they alternate the language

00:52:38.320 --> 00:52:40.150
of instruction from day to day.

00:52:40.150 --> 00:52:43.510
And the kids are supposed to
be fluent in both languages

00:52:43.510 --> 00:52:46.150
by the time they're
in fifth grade.

00:52:46.150 --> 00:52:49.450
